Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.82,0:01:36.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救救夜卜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.78,0:01:38.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夜…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.24,0:01:39.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一线
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.79,0:01:44.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,境界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.25,0:01:49.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么啊 求你打开它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.71,0:01:51.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大黑先生 小福小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.38,0:01:55.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求求你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.05,0:01:59.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夜卜他…夜卜他快死了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.52,0:02:08.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日和只有你一个人过来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.15,0:02:15.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小福 你带日和去洗净恙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.20,0:02:22.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些水是直接将庭院里的净水引进来的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.24,0:02:24.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 洗洗身体吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.95,0:02:26.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这给也让夜卜洗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.75,0:02:29.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夜卜就算洗这个也来不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.38,0:02:31.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来不及…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.96,0:02:36.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪 他得接受惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.68,0:02:43.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【第9话 名字】
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.81,0:02:46.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小福 这里麻烦你看顾了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.85,0:02:49.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去附近的神社转转
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.35,0:02:51.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.90,0:02:53.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪音的惩罚是指什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.19,0:02:54.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是「禊」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.15,0:02:59.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「禊」是除尽恙的仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.78,0:03:01.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个仪式需要3名神器
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.24,0:03:03.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了我以外还需要两名神器
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.24,0:03:09.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该明白一但禊失败的话 会有什么后果...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.58,0:03:14.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之得赶紧把神器带来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.84,0:03:22.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样子没法拖到明早了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.72,0:03:24.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪音
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.06,0:03:28.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要你敢移动一步 我就打死你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.15,0:03:36.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鬼理你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.37,0:03:49.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.67,0:03:56.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夜卜可能真的会死
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.59,0:04:00.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 雪音一定要接受的惩罚到底是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.55,0:04:04.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请一定 一定要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.76,0:04:06.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救救他们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.52,0:04:13.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 神明和神器...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.44,0:04:16.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又有谁能拯救他们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.82,0:04:20.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夜卜他…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.20,0:04:22.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.91,0:04:26.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,禊什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.41,0:04:29.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要稍有差池就会被妖怪吃掉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.12,0:04:31.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被妖怪吃掉？！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.62,0:04:33.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有一个朋友也是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.21,0:04:36.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子帮忙进行一个严重的禊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.54,0:04:38.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子最后怎样了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.25,0:04:40.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.01,0:04:43.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为那次之后他就没回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.89,0:04:48.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果您允许 请让我前往
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.76,0:04:52.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 你在说什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.52,0:04:56.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他终究是曾经赐予我「伴」此名之人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.77,0:04:57.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.02,0:04:58.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你叫…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.98,0:04:59.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真喻
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.94,0:05:02.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们还需要一位
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.07,0:05:12.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,承蒙您出手相助 大恩大德我大黑必定铭记在心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.25,0:05:15.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也请各位姐姐多加注意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.33,0:05:17.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别让道真大人身体染恙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.42,0:05:24.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.05,0:05:28.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你堕落了吗 夜卜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.97,0:05:31.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这笨蛋 到底在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.47,0:05:36.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求求您 求您务必借出一名神器
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.31,0:05:38.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求您务必要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.90,0:05:39.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求您
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.19,0:05:43.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算派遣神器前去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.82,0:05:46.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不能保证能在主人堕落的情况下得救
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.61,0:05:51.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说到底 那种能将主人刺伤到这个地步的神器
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.54,0:05:55.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斩了雪音吧 夜卜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.30,0:06:03.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大黑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.97,0:06:08.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还差一名神器
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.43,0:06:11.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这该怎么办啊? 大黑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.68,0:06:15.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之 我会再转转看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.39,0:06:16.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.10,0:06:20.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挂了 再联络吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.86,0:06:24.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这附近的神还剩…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.91,0:06:31.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.58,0:06:35.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么下去小夜卜会…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.49,0:06:36.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死掉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.63,0:06:49.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还差一名
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.38,0:06:52.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还得再找一名神器
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.35,0:06:56.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是野良的话 一定会为了夜卜前来的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.98,0:07:00.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 她一定会...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.31,0:07:05.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要是挡路的 不管是啥我都可以漂亮的砍掉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.98,0:07:07.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,砍了雪音
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.15,0:07:09.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.37,0:07:19.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是再遇到威娜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.12,0:07:22.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是毘沙门 你就当看不见
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.00,0:07:24.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你还想要活命的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.97,0:07:31.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.10,0:07:36.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兆麻先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.56,0:07:37.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兆麻先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.77,0:07:38.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兆麻先生～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.48,0:07:43.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艮一方有何异常
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.48,0:07:46.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目前尚无风穴打开的痕迹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.40,0:07:48.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巽一方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.69,0:07:50.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有任何问题
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.53,0:07:52.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会继续对那里警备的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.78,0:07:54.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兆麻哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.20,0:07:59.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…我从刚才就听到有人不断喊兆麻哥哥的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.50,0:08:00.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了吗 兆麻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.04,0:08:03.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.88,0:08:08.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种连一击都不做的无礼之徒 别管他就好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.26,0:08:12.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续汇报吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.72,0:08:13.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兆麻先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.80,0:08:16.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求求你 助我们一臂之力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.01,0:08:18.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兆麻先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.26,0:08:19.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兆麻先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.43,0:08:20.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兆…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.77,0:08:23.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然没找齐？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.77,0:08:25.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋笨蛋笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.40,0:08:26.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的有认真找过了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.02,0:08:28.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的有找过啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.86,0:08:33.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是没有一个肯为了一个不知名的神明的神器前来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.70,0:08:35.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请振作 夜卜大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.07,0:08:36.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夜卜大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.78,0:08:38.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}该怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.16,0:08:41.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.00,0:08:43.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是让你一动不动待那儿么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.71,0:08:44.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁管你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.17,0:08:49.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.13,0:08:50.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兆麻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.80,0:08:52.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.47,0:08:54.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夜卜怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.59,0:08:58.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是夜卜的敌人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.60,0:09:01.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 但我还差他一个人情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.73,0:09:05.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 是那女孩叫我来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.60,0:09:07.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小日和
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.44,0:09:10.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们也说说她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.94,0:09:12.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明明警告过她的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.28,0:09:13.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么大喇喇的直接前来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.53,0:09:15.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是被威娜发现的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.78,0:09:16.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会被袭击的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.58,0:09:21.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不知道他于你有什么有恩情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.83,0:09:23.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 这下就有3名神器了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.12,0:09:25.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 他的这种情况下…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.38,0:09:32.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伤势相当严重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.22,0:09:35.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夜卜 能听到我说话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.63,0:09:38.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,取走雪音的名字把他赶走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.80,0:09:40.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你身上的恙入侵的太深了 你撑不过去的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.06,0:09:44.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夜卜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.60,0:09:47.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他从刚才开始就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.65,0:09:50.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 只能进行禊了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.11,0:09:53.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪音 你做过什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.90,0:09:55.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没做什么啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.32,0:09:58.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你为什么想离开这里?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.24,0:10:00.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想怎么样都不关你的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.78,0:10:04.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道不是因为心生愧疚么?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.58,0:10:06.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你们太烦了 每个人都是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.96,0:10:08.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都说了我什么都没做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.67,0:10:13.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 那你把上衣脱掉看看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.38,0:10:15.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈 为什么我非要脱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.55,0:10:17.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 闭嘴脱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.65,0:10:33.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这是什么?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.36,0:10:37.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你小子居然将主人刺伤到这个程度
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.61,0:10:39.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}「悲鸣... 好冷...」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.86,0:10:39.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们都有相当觉悟了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.70,0:10:42.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮我拿下来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.16,0:10:44.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快帮我拿下来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.37,0:10:52.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敬献于夜卜神 拭去御灵 守护御名
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.50,0:10:54.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸 什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.00,0:10:57.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,清除污秽 化世俗之心于无
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.30,0:11:00.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明亮 率真 正直之魂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.38,0:11:02.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反复行禊 净之化之
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.56,0:11:05.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.08,0:11:25.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.29,0:11:29.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,禊是指洁净身体
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.91,0:11:32.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是神器利用境界线进行的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.88,0:11:33.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,私刑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.92,0:11:36.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,私…刑…是指
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.92,0:11:40.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神器犯了罪孽也只能由原本为人的神器来惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.22,0:11:41.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放了我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.18,0:11:43.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放我出来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.47,0:11:49.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦禊开始了就不能中断
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.56,0:11:53.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到神器将自己所有的罪孽全盘托出
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.44,0:11:55.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进行忏悔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.19,0:11:58.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪音 你干什么坏事了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.40,0:11:59.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.36,0:12:02.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴 我杀了你胡子男
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.03,0:12:03.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否则的话...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.96,0:12:13.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了 要变化为妖了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.60,0:12:31.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.60,0:12:33.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快住手 这样太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.98,0:12:34.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太残忍了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.90,0:12:40.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我到底做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.48,0:12:42.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我什么错都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.70,0:12:44.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,错的不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.12,0:12:52.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过为了那么点小钱 就这样...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.75,0:12:59.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 我偷了 抢了 砸了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.80,0:13:01.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那又怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.55,0:13:04.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们也明白的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.13,0:13:06.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我们都死了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.26,0:13:11.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为...因为那些家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.93,0:13:13.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.27,0:13:15.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟父母吵架了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.35,0:13:16.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我让哥哥帮忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.73,0:13:17.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.19,0:13:20.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}[加油 加油]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.78,0:13:26.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未来 回忆 家人 朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.78,0:13:28.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些家伙明明都有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.82,0:13:30.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么就我没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.08,0:13:36.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么就我什么都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.96,0:13:43.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.38,0:13:46.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发觉过来 自己已是孤身一人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.63,0:13:49.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我什么都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.01,0:13:50.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都没...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.60,0:13:54.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是美丽的双瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.60,0:13:57.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像风中摇曳的山楂果实
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.31,0:14:03.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 这果实连鸟儿都不吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.86,0:14:06.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非甜非苦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.15,0:14:09.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽无毒 却也于身体无益
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.53,0:14:13.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无一是处的中空果实
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.54,0:14:17.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连鸟儿都不曾啄食一口 便悄然褪色
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.17,0:14:19.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无所牵连
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.92,0:14:23.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到干瘪消逝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.97,0:14:28.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是可怜的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.85,0:14:43.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夺取这一切有什么不对?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.77,0:14:45.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毁坏这一切有什么不对?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.61,0:14:49.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家 如果都像我这样...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.57,0:14:53.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死掉就好!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.68,0:15:15.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了 再这样下去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.01,0:15:18.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大黑 快化黑器打倒他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.23,0:15:21.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别慌 呆子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.10,0:15:23.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一抽手这里不就溃决了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.15,0:15:25.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,况且 化黑器就会时化
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.73,0:15:27.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有什么意义
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.65,0:15:29.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就没什么更好的办法了吗 业界精英
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.42,0:15:43.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,印记...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.21,0:15:46.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那要是被吞噬了的话 就...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.25,0:15:47.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.39,0:15:56.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名字
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.47,0:16:00.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不呼唤...那家伙的名字的话...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.56,0:16:04.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名字就会消失...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.74,0:16:16.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎么说 都是我看中的家伙嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.12,0:16:24.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就会走去那边...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.71,0:16:27.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名字...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.55,0:16:30.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名字...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.23,0:16:43.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪音
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.69,0:16:44.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小日和
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.35,0:16:46.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危险 快退后
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.86,0:16:48.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪音 不能去那边
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.36,0:16:51.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请不要变成妖怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.37,0:17:03.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪音 你不是有夜卜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.91,0:17:07.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪音 应该也听到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.83,0:17:09.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然这家伙是个不中用的混蛋小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.13,0:17:12.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但 他是被我找到 由我命名的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.26,0:17:16.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪器 由我来磨练
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.72,0:17:20.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些话 就像父亲一样...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.35,0:17:29.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夜卜 夜卜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.73,0:17:32.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算不断被雪音背叛 被刺伤
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.40,0:17:34.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也一直承受著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.95,0:17:37.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果继续背叛那样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.57,0:17:41.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就不和你做朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.41,0:17:46.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朋...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.71,0:17:48.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.68,0:17:58.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪音
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.85,0:18:06.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实 你已无法和此岸的人...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.89,0:18:09.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保持对等的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.44,0:18:13.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 雪音
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.74,0:18:16.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我给了你人的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.28,0:18:21.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.74,0:18:24.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以作为一个人活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.12,0:18:27.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要活下去 雪音
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.05,0:18:38.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对...对...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.72,0:18:40.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.35,0:18:48.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不...对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.39,0:18:50.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我刺伤了夜卜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.56,0:18:51.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也偷了钱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.27,0:18:56.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还想...偷摸日和
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.53,0:18:59.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还偷了滑板
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.32,0:19:01.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又打碎了玻璃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.78,0:19:04.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撒了很多谎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.50,0:19:08.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我再也不那样了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.00,0:19:14.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的...真的 很对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.50,0:19:16.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.33,0:19:50.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 两个人都没问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.33,0:19:53.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还以为要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.17,0:19:54.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经死了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.67,0:19:58.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我才讨厌惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.84,0:20:01.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了我家笨蛋真是抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.47,0:20:02.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,道声谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.93,0:20:04.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.35,0:20:08.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对日和也是 真没想到会给你添这么多麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.93,0:20:10.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.06,0:20:11.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你给我过来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.56,0:20:15.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.15,0:20:17.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也给我道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.77,0:20:19.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 日和
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.45,0:20:26.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果 她没带我来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.24,0:20:28.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也许就那样死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.04,0:20:34.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果 她带来的神器是野良
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.29,0:20:36.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也许会因无法忍受痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.09,0:20:39.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用野良斩了雪音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.92,0:20:44.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果 她没有叫回雪音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.68,0:20:48.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果 没有日和的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.81,0:20:51.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.77,0:20:56.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救了我们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.77,0:21:00.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.86,0:21:03.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两个都没事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.82,0:21:10.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对...对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.00,0:21:13.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日和
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.72,0:21:28.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你们...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.98,0:23:15.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}【注：日本童谣，常在玩装鬼游戏时唱，大概是说白天煮熟吃掉的东西，会变成妖怪夜里出现】
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.98,0:23:08.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冒泡泡了 煮熟了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.40,0:23:13.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,煮熟了没 尝尝看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.45,0:23:15.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吧唧 吧唧 吧唧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.12,0:23:21.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为那孩子会被妖怪吧唧吧唧吃掉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.34,0:23:26.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然让你醒来是正确的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.26,0:23:28.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗坊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.72,0:23:34.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冒泡泡了 煮熟了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.47,0:23:37.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,煮熟了没 尝尝看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.23,0:23:40.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经煮熟了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.73,0:23:43.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夜卜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.56,0:23:48.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那真是过去的祸津神...夜卜吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.53,0:23:53.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你自己去确认下不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.04,0:24:00.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下回 野良神 应忌讳之人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.00,0:24:02.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是 初次见面 我是真喻
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.00,0:24:04.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说这是初次见面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.25,0:24:05.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是大黑
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.17,0:24:05.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是兆麻
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.84,0:24:07.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 我就此告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.38,0:24:07.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.96,0:24:09.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.96,0:24:12.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那两人 意外地像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.94,0:23:25.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}【童谣歌词：http://www.worldfolksong.com/songbook/japan/warabeuta/abukutatta.htm】
