Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.72,0:22:21.26,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}所以我踏上了旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.35,0:22:23.81,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}去向境界线
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.10,0:22:28.85,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}若是如此  我将
