Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.29,0:22:49.37,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}请紧握这双手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.46,0:22:51.25,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}请不要离开
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.25,0:22:59.47,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你已不再是一个人
